---
import '../styles/main.css';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alegreya+Sans:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Joe Murphy</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="wrapper">
			<h1>Joe Murphy</h1>
			<p>Design Facilitation · Consulting · Research</p>
			<ul>
				<li>MSC IT-Product Design</li>
				<li>Jr. Data Scientist</li>
				<li>BA Industrial Design</li>
			</ul>
		</header>

		<main class="[ wrapper ]">
			<section class="flow">
				<h2>Design facilitation for Teams & Product Development</h2>
				<p>I explore human insights through participatory research and co-design 
				methods to help teams and organizations create meaningful, user-centered 
				solutions. I facilitate workshops, strategy sessions, and collaborative 
				design processes that enhance team alignment, improve user experiences, 
				and drive innovation.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="flow">
				<h2>Overview</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>As a design facilitator, I build and lead teams in creating human-centred solutions that align services and products with real user needs, helping organisations thrive. My work blends design thinking, strategic insight, and empathy-driven research to generate impactful product and service designs. I design a tailored process for the team and facilitate collaborative workshops to foster strategic alignment across diverse teams and deeply immerse myself in each project, examining the full user and operational experience. Through prototyping and testing, I ensure that solutions are innovative, sustainable, and ready for real-world application.</li>
					<li>I also support clients by building their internal design capabilities, empowering teams to innovate independently and create enduring change aligned with their mission. In addition to design, facilitation, and coaching, I collaborate with academia on design anthropology, researching cognitive theories related to spatial setups for effective collaboration.</li>
					<li>As a design facilitator, I build and guide teams to create human-centred solutions that align services and products with real user needs. My work blends design thinking, strategic insight and empathy-driven research.</li>
					<li>I strengthen internal design capabilities by designing bespoke processes for your team and by facilitating collaborative workshops across organisations. To create mission-aligned, sustainable change, I empower teams to innovate independently.</li>
					<li>Through collaboration with design anthropology academia, I study cognitive theories related to spatial configurations for effective collaboration.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="flow">
				<h2>What I Do</h2>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Uncover user needs & insights</strong> – Using participatory research to inform design decisions.</li>
					<li><strong>Facilitate co-design workshops</strong> – Helping teams collaborate, innovate, and develop strategies together.</li>
					<li><strong>Support sustainability & well-being</strong> – Designing for long-term impact on people and the planet.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="flow">
				<h2>Services Offered</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<strong>Service Design</strong><br>
						Designing end-to-end service experiences with a focus on user-centered solutions that enhance customer satisfaction and business effectiveness.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Design Research</strong><br>
						Conducting qualitative and quantitative research to uncover actionable insights about users, market needs, and service opportunities.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Workshop Design & Facilitation</strong><br>
						Creating and leading interactive workshops to foster stakeholder engagement, team alignment, and creative problem-solving.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Capability Building & Live Learning</strong><br>
						Embedding within teams to transfer service design skills, helping organizations to independently drive and sustain design innovation
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Prototyping & Testing</strong><br>
						Developing and iteratively testing service prototypes to validate ideas and refine them based on real-world feedback
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="flow">
				<h2>Frequent Deliverables</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>
						<strong>Customer Journey Maps</strong><br>
						Visual representations of customer experiences to identify pain points, opportunities, and key moments of engagement.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Service Blueprints</strong><br>
						Comprehensive maps of service processes, detailing both customer-facing and behind-the-scenes interactions to ensure smooth, integrated service delivery.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Personas & User Profiles</strong><br>
						Detailed profiles of key user segments, based on research, to guide empathetic and targeted design decisions.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Insights Reports</strong><br>
						In-depth research summaries highlighting key user insights, patterns, and strategic recommendations.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Prototypes & Mockups</strong><br>
						Interactive prototypes that showcase proposed service features and allow for hands-on user testing and refinement.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Training Materials & Toolkits</strong><br>
						Custom-designed resources that empower teams to adopt and maintain a service design mindset and process.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Workshop & Facilitation Reports</strong><br>
						Summaries of workshop outcomes, including participant feedback, identified solutions, and strategic next steps.
					</li>
					<li>
						<strong>Design Guidelines & Documentation</strong><br>
						Clear guidelines and documentation to support the ongoing implementation and scaling of service solutions across the organization.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<p>I believe the best solutions come from understanding people deeply and designing with them, not just for them. Let's connect and explore new ways to create meaningful experiences!</p>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
